Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.64,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,A pocket of romance, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.58,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are!
